<br>
Ive managed to work him up to level 23, been hunting in lake of ill omen.  <br>
<br>
Looking for general advice on what items to try and aim for weapon wise and armor wise.<br>
<br>
Also looking for advice on the delecite art of PULLING and tanking in general.  So far ive managed to only die once in my 23 levels and have saved a group on numorous occasions (guess luck favors the foolish cause ive done some really stupid stunts as a warrior but had a blast doing them, like at lv 21 &quot;yea, i can tank that Avocet&quot; hehe, turned out i had to bow kite him while the group ran to the zone, then Sow ran out, made it to zone with 8 hp but was fun. too many other stories of insane heroism that i survived and do not know how.<br>
<br>
Anyway just advice on Equipment/Stats/Weapons (what should i look for in a weapon? speed or damage and what is the optimum ratio for speed and damage?<br>
<br>
